										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/mason-jones-9e_ssIz4jB4-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>車子啟動前需要注意周遭環境！日前有一名女子分享自身的離奇經歷，某日她在準備開車時，意外在車輪鋁圈上發現一隻熟睡的流浪小貓，女子隨即將小貓安全引出並暫時收留，才避免了一場憾事發生，暖心舉動讓網友們驚呼「真的差點出大事」。&nbsp;</p>



<p>該名女子表示，當天她正準備開車出門時，如往常般地在啟動前檢查車子，注意到輪胎鋁圈內似乎卡著一片橘紅色的落葉，便打算伸手將其取下，卻沒想到走近一看，才發現自己原先認為所謂的「落葉」竟是一隻小小的流浪貓咪。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="814" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C814&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-239736" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1025&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1366&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/chris-yang-pjy6SHm3JEk-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">小貓目前已被暫時安置，女子猜測牠可能真的太累才會躲在輪胎內休息<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>小貓蜷縮著熟睡在鋁圈內，對周遭的環境全無察覺，讓女子感到有些詫異，猜測小貓可能因長期流浪過於疲累，才選擇這個危險又狹窄的地方休息，她輕輕撫摸著貓咪並耐心將其誘導出來，隨後暫時為小貓安排了安置處，等待後續能幫牠找到合適的領養家庭。&nbsp;</p>



<p>女子分享的自身經歷迅速引起網友們熱烈討論，不少人紛紛感謝她的細心與善良，並留言表示「開車前真的要好好檢查」、「小貓應該太累了」、「輪胎內很髒一般貓咪不太會願意待在那」、「好險車主有發現」、「如果直接開車後果恐將不堪設想」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/11/%e9%96%8b%e8%bb%8a%e5%89%8d%e8%a6%81%e5%b0%8f%e5%bf%83%ef%bc%81%e7%9c%bc%e5%b0%96%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90%e7%99%bc%e7%8f%be%e8%bc%aa%e8%83%8e%e8%97%8f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e3%80%80%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e5%a4%a7/">開車前要小心！眼尖女子發現輪胎藏小貓　網友大讚：差點出大事 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
